keepConnect.name: Bikala ya kukangama
keepConnect.helperText: Kana nge niema na kisika bo me sonika Kuyantika, na nima bumba lien yina. Yo ke lombaka nde bo tula dikebi nde bo vukisa diaka lien yina ntangu yonso na nima ya kukatula yo.
